Package: replicationOrigins
Type: Package
Title: Functions used for replication origin detection and evaluation
Version: 1.0
Author: Roman Jaksik
Maintainer: Roman Jaksik <roman.jaksik@polsl.pl>
Encoding: UTF-8
License: file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Description: This package contains functions used to detect replication origins based on PMA score (somatic mutation pattern) and RFD profiles (OK-seq data). The package also contains function used to compare two or more sets of numerical vectors using an algorithm similar to Nedleman-Wunsh global alignment.
